{"id": "1182760510341533796", "channel_id": "1182040346234982483", "type": 0, "author_id": "1172138340275994645", "author_name": "cpeax_34497", "author_bot": false, "content": "連克蘇魯都變成圖魯那樣的傢伙了，伊斯人會被困在這個世界想必也很正常罷…不過有一點我很好奇，溶蝕會讓外神和古神也忘掉那些被融掉的人嗎😆", "timestamp": "2023-12-08T19:08:00.293000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1182040346234982483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[克蘇魯神話元素] 溫柯爾裡面的人", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1182776015978770464", "channel_id": "1182040346234982483", "type": 0, "author_id": "632796667896266782", "author_name": "xuanbugaimingkebujiufei", "author_bot": false, "content": "朵爾那個大腦應該是米戈的缸中之腦科技。\n\n伊斯不是怕飛天水螅，是他現在佔據的種族，身體是對方的主食，比起怕更像噁心，畢竟對方整天想吃他，又搞不死，只能封印。\n他們本身逼格還蠻高的，一佔據這個種族就把天敵飛天水螅給封印了\n對方破封也在他們掌握之內\n伊斯所求只有知識，如果真的拿伊斯當參照，以因為好奇所以不想走，與當地生物達成合作，會是比較正常的敘述。\n基本上大多數種族都是忌憚伊斯的，除非能免疫精神控制或是讓伊斯無法理解你的思維，比方飛天水螅。", "timestamp": "2023-12-08T20:09:37.125000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1182040346234982483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[克蘇魯神話元素] 溫柯爾裡面的人", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1182777858658156587", "channel_id": "1182040346234982483", "type": 19, "author_id": "632796667896266782", "author_name": "xuanbugaimingkebujiufei", "author_bot": false, "content": "克蘇魯不可能是圖魯，頂多是大袞。\n外神逼格不是目前的溶蝕能比的，古神還有點可能\n但也有可能他用世界觀壓制，畢竟這劇情重點是溶蝕", "timestamp": "2023-12-08T20:16:56.454000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1172138340275994645"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1182760510341533796", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1182040346234982483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[克蘇魯神話元素] 溫柯爾裡面的人", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1182778229900181604", "channel_id": "1182040346234982483", "type": 0, "author_id": "632796667896266782", "author_name": "xuanbugaimingkebujiufei", "author_bot": false, "content": "想這個其實沒啥意義\n他是參考克蘇魯元素\n世界觀還是官方說了算", "timestamp": "2023-12-08T20:18:24.965000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1182040346234982483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[克蘇魯神話元素] 溫柯爾裡面的人", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1182780176325693470", "channel_id": "1182040346234982483", "type": 0, "author_id": "632796667896266782", "author_name": "xuanbugaimingkebujiufei", "author_bot": false, "content": "不然真要帶入克蘇魯神話\n大機率是奈亞拉托提普在找樂子\n就像你拿水去灌蟻穴一樣\n神不在意\nSAN=0只是正要開始瞭解世界罷了", "timestamp": "2023-12-08T20:26:09.029000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1182040346234982483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[克蘇魯神話元素] 溫柯爾裡面的人", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1182786844518269038", "channel_id": "1182040346234982483", "type": 19, "author_id": "1172138340275994645", "author_name": "cpeax_34497", "author_bot": false, "content": "我還是比較期望真正出一個照面就是sc1d10/1d100的傢伙來當隊員的😆不過遊戲好像跟克蘇魯神話只是蹭蹭不進去的關係😇", "timestamp": "2023-12-08T20:52:38.850000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["632796667896266782"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1182778229900181604", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1182040346234982483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[克蘇魯神話元素] 溫柯爾裡面的人", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
